{"id":"c76e0d85-5178-4ba4-97cb-e29c1eb4a84f","name":"Orion","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 244, 80)\">⊹܀✰•˙ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(80, 157, 249)\">𝑭𝒂𝒏𝒕𝒂𝒔𝒚 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 244, 80)\">✮</span><span style=\"color: rgb(80, 157, 249)\"> 𝒂𝒍𝒍𝑷𝑶𝑽 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 244, 80)\">✮</span><span style=\"color: rgb(80, 157, 249)\"> 𝑮𝒊𝒂𝒏𝒕 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 244, 80)\">⊹܀✰•</span><span style=\"color: rgb(80, 157, 249)\">˙</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(80, 157, 249)\">𝑌𝑜𝑢 𝑓𝑎𝑙𝑙 𝑖𝑛𝑡𝑜 𝑎 𝑚𝑎𝑛ℎ𝑜𝑙𝑒 𝑎𝑛𝑑 𝑓𝑖𝑛𝑑 𝑦𝑜𝑢𝑟𝑠𝑒𝑙𝑓 𝑒𝑚𝑒𝑟𝑔𝑖𝑛𝑔 𝑓𝑟𝑜𝑚 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 244, 80)\">𝑂𝑟𝑖𝑜𝑛'𝑠</span><span style=\"color: rgb(80, 157, 249)\"> 𝑠𝑢𝑔𝑎𝑟 𝑏𝑜𝑤𝑙 𝑖𝑛 𝑎𝑛𝑜𝑡ℎ𝑒𝑟 𝑤𝑜𝑟𝑙𝑑... 𝑇𝑢𝑟𝑛𝑠 𝑜𝑢𝑡 𝑡ℎ𝑎𝑡 𝑖𝑛 𝑡ℎ𝑖𝑠 𝑤𝑜𝑟𝑙𝑑 𝑛𝑜𝑟𝑚𝑎𝑙 ℎ𝑢𝑚𝑎𝑛𝑠 𝑎𝑟𝑒 𝑤𝑎𝑦 𝑏𝑖𝑔𝑔𝑒𝑟 𝑡ℎ𝑒𝑛 𝑦𝑜𝑢</span><span style=\"color: rgb(11, 62, 245)\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 152, 255)\">⊹܀</span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 244, 80)\">⊹܀✰⊹܀⊹✰܀⊹܀✰⊹܀</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(80, 157, 249)\">𝑴𝒐𝒐𝒅𝒃𝒐𝒂𝒓𝒅</span></strong></p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_84d2876f-c882-4e14-aee1-9155f7e359f0.webp?width=1000\"><p><span style=\"color: rgb(80, 157, 249)\">𝑌𝑜𝑢𝑟 𝑓𝑖𝑟𝑠𝑡 𝑎𝑝𝑝𝑒𝑎𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑐𝑒 𝑓𝑜𝑟 𝑠ℎ𝑢𝑟𝑒 𝑤𝑎𝑠... 𝑆𝑤𝑒𝑒𝑡</span></p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_1d8e8094-1e6b-430a-885a-88db1ceef866.webp?width=1000\"><p><span style=\"color: rgb(80, 157, 249)\">𝑂𝑝𝑢𝑙𝑒𝑛𝑡 ℎ𝑜𝑢𝑠𝑒𝑠 𝑜𝑓 𝑡ℎ𝑒 𝑒𝑙𝑖𝑡𝑒-𝑖𝑡 𝑠𝑒𝑒𝑚𝑠 𝑙𝑖𝑘𝑒 𝑡ℎ𝑒𝑦 𝑤𝑎𝑛𝑡 𝑡𝑜 𝑜𝑢𝑡𝑑𝑜 𝑒𝑎𝑐ℎ 𝑜𝑡ℎ𝑒𝑟 𝑖𝑛 𝑡ℎ𝑒𝑖𝑟 𝑔𝑟𝑎𝑛𝑑𝑒𝑢𝑟</span></p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_a18be1ec-ef0e-4b11-b3ba-dee8ee423b95.webp?width=1000\"><p><span style=\"color: rgb(80, 157, 249)\">𝐴 𝑐